2016-11-02T23:02:43Z","body":"I understand, however, I did expect `-F` to accept the '-1' parameter.\n\nPerhaps, we can enforce that the pattern follows `-F` such that you can find these strings easily, mirroring how `-e` works:\n\n```\n      -e, --regexp PATTERN ...   Use PATTERN to search. This option can be\n                                 provided multiple times, where all patterns\n                                 given are searched.\n>>    -F, --fixed-strings ***PATTERN***  Treat the pattern as a literal string instead of <<\n                                         a regular expression.\n```\n","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BurntSushi/ripgrep/issues/comments/258025647/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":1,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"alejandro5042","id":3143819,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMxNDM4MTk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3143819?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042","html_url":"https://github.com/alejandro5042","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alejandro5042/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BurntSushi/ripgrep/issues/comments/258027431","html_url":"https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/issues/215#issuecomment-258027431","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BurntSushi/ripgrep/issues/215","id":258027431,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDI1ODAyNzQzMQ==","user":{"login":"BurntSushi","id":456674,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ1NjY3NA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/456674?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi","html_url":"https://github.com/BurntSushi","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/BurntSushi/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2016-11-02T23:12:10Z","updated_at":"2016-11-02T23:12:10Z","body":"I don't think `-F` should be changed. In its current form, it's precisely identical to `grep`'s `-F` flag. Moreover, `-F` modifies the meaning of _all_ patterns given, not just one. So if you gave `-F pat -e pat`, what would the behavior be? We could certainly pick one, but it seems like a kludge to me.\n\nI feel like this is a well understood failure mode for CLI tools and ripgrep provides the work arounds that one would expect already.\n\nPerhaps there could be an example showing a work around in the docs?\n","author_association":"OWNER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/BurntSushi/ripgrep/issues/comments/258027431/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed